                 <option value="CHAIRPERSON">अध्यक्ष (Chairperson Slot)</option>
                 <option value="CHIEF">हालका प्रमुख (Chief Slot)</option>
                 <option value="INFO_OFFICER">सूचना अधिकारी (Info Officer Slot)</option>
